io.doov.core.dsl.impl.base

Class StringFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.doov.core.dsl.impl.DefaultFunction<java.lang.String,PredicateMetadata>
      • io.doov.core.dsl.impl.base.StringFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextAccessor<java.lang.String>, Function<java.lang.String>, DSLBuilder, MappingInput<java.lang.String>, Readable

    public class StringFunction
extends DefaultFunction<java.lang.String,PredicateMetadata>
    Base class for string conditions.

    It contains a DslField to get the value from the model, a StringFunctionMetadata to describe this node, and a BiFunction to take the value from the model and return an optional value.
